	* src/plugins/DefinedTunnelingCoefficients.cpp: modified for new plugin
	parsing format
	* examplesSchema/DefinedTunellingCoefficients,
	examplesSchema/DefinedTunellingCoefficients/OH+methanol.xml: updated

