2013-April-08 Chris Morley

	Use different bath gases in the same run
	* src/plugins/ExponentialDown.cpp,
	src/EnergyTransferModel.h,src/plugins/GaussianModel.cpp: 
	parse for deltaEDown for specified bath gases
	 
